      "content": "it just feels so pointless. i've lived a long life, i've done what i was supposed to do, but now there's nothing left but this constant, slow decline. i don't want to spend my last months just waiting for the inevitable. i feel like i've lost all my dignity, just being a burden and waiting for a natural end that might take way longer than it should. i wish i had some kind of control over it all.",
